Constructor Detail

TahitiDialog

protected TahitiDialog(javax.swing.JFrame parentFrame)
Creates the dialog window displaying the main components. Please note that the dialog window will have a main component, called content panel, at the center and a button panel at the south where user can add buttons. Moreover there will be standard buttons at the south for managing the ok/cancel operation.

Parameters:
parentFrame - the frame owner of this dialog.

protected final void showText(java.lang.String message)

Parameters:
message - the message to show (must be not-null)
